    Card
    Creates all the standard cards to be used in standard decks including 4 suites and 13 ranks for a total of 52 standard cards.

    Keeps track of the top of the deck
    Poker
    Original poker game, has a few bugs, fixed mostly in PokerUtil and Poker2
    Poker2  
    PokerUtility
    Poker Utility that can be used to compare decks to determine which deck wins, as well as compare two decks Can also be used to determine if a deck meets a certain case;
    RunGame  
    TableTop
    Table top provides the jPanel to serve as a table top for the developer to place game objects like cards, buttons, scores.
    War
    The game of war uses two standard decks of cards, one for each player.
